                                                                                <https://hcis.io/ontology/aicapstone/2026/TaskRole> ;
                                                                       rdfs:comment "A task role individual representing the ReferenceObject role. Assigned to objects that anchor the spatial layout without being grasped."@en ;
                                                                       rdfs:label "reference object role"@en ;
                                                                       <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Instances of this role provide a fixed pose frame used to compute placement targets for other objects; the robot reads their pose but does not grasp them."@en .


